</script><section class="hero"><div class="ui basic video modal"><div class="video-container"><script src="//fast.wistia.com/embed/medias/k6gl2kt2eq.jsonp" async></script><script src="//fast.wistia.com/assets/external/E-v1.js" async></script><div style="padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;" class="wistia_responsive_padding"><div style="height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%;" class="wistia_responsive_wrapper"><div style="height:100%;width:100%" class="wistia_embed wistia_async_k6gl2kt2eq autoPlay=true videoFoam=true"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="content video-hero"><div class="copy-container smaller"><h1>Modernize your recruiting process</h1><p>End-to-end recruiting software to help you attract & hire great employees with less effort</p><a href="/signup" class="button green medium">Get started for free</a></div><div class="video-right-container"><a class="video-thumb-button"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/breezyhr-assets/images/marketing/video/video_thumb.png" alt="Hire more awesome" class="large"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/breezyhr-assets/images/marketing/video/video_thumb_sm.png" alt="Hire more awesome" class="small"><i class="fa fa-play-circle"></i></a></div><script>$('.video.modal').modal('attach events', '.video-thumb-button', 'show');</script></div></section><section class="features-screenshot-left top-skew"><div class="wow fadeInLeft"><div class="content"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-7 first-md last-xs"><div class="feature-image browser-cap dragdrop"><video id="dragdrop" preload="auto" autoplay loop poster="//s3.amazonaws.com/breezyhr-assets/images/marketing/v4/video/dragdrop.jpg" class="video-js"><source src="//s3.amazonaws.com/breezyhr-assets/images/marketing/v4/video/dragdrop.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video></div></div><div class="col-md-5 bigger"><h4>&nbsp;</h4><h2>A bird's-eye view of your candidate pipeline</h2><p>Our drag & drop pipeline management means you know at a glance who‚Äôs at what stage in your pipeline:</p><ul class="list-items"><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Customize your pipeline stages per position</div></li><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Automate your common tasks with Stage Actions</div></li><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Upload or email in candidates individually or in bulk</div></li><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Consistent candidate interviewing & scoring with custom Scorecards & Interview Guides</div></li></ul><br><br><br></div></div></div></div></section><section class="promotions grey"><div class="content"><h4>post to 40+ job boards with one-click</h4><div class="row sites center-xs"><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/indeed.png" class="site indeed"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/linkedin.png" class="site linkedin"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/glassdoor.png" class="site glassdoor"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/monster.png" class="site monster"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/stackoverflow.png" class="site stackoverflow"></div></div><div class="row sites center-xs middle"><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/google.png" class="site indeed"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/wayup.png" class="site linkedin"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/careerbuilder.png" class="site glassdoor"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/dice.png" class="site monster"></div><div class="col-md col-xs-12"><img src="/images/marketing/jobboards/ziprecruiter.png" class="site ziprecruiter"></div></div></div></section><section class="features-screenshot-right"><div class="wow fadeInRight"><div class="content"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-5"><h4></h4><h2>Streamline candidate communication and interview scheduling</h2><p>Breezy includes all the tools you and your team need to work together scheduling and vetting candidates.</p><ul class="list-items"><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Talk to your team in-app, so you always have the most up-to-date conversations on hand</div></li><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Integrate your GMail and Office 365 conversations with ease</div></li><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Create bulk and individual emails, even custom templates, on the fly</div></li><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i><div>Let your candidates pick the best available time with self-scheduling</div></li></ul></div><div class="col-md-7"><div class="feature-image browser-cap bigger emailconversation"><video id="emailconversation" preload="auto" autoplay loop poster="//s3.amazonaws.com/breezyhr-assets/images/marketing/v4/video/emailconversation.jpg" class="video-js"><source src="//s3.amazonaws.com/breezyhr-assets/images/marketing/v4/video/emailconversation.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="pop-quotes orange"><div class="content"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-4"><div class="pop-quote pop-quote-1 wow rubberBand"><blockquote><p>The most user friendly tool I have used thus far in my recruiting career!</p></blockquote><div class="pop-quote-person"><div class="pop-quote-avatar"><img src="https://assets-cdn.breezy.hr/breezy-hr/customers/nandos-peri-peri/jackie-phillipson.jpg"></div><div class="pop-quote-info"><div class="pop-quote-name">Jackie Phillipson, <br/>Nando‚Äôs Peri-Peri</div></div></div></div><div class="pop-quote pop-quote-1 wow rubberBand"><blockquote><p>Beautiful job site, stays focused on what they do best: source through hire, constant updates and new features, excellent customer support.</p></blockquote><div class="pop-quote-person"><div class="pop-quote-avatar"><img src="https://media-exp2.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_400_400/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAjYAAAAJDg2NDNhMTI1LTRlMDYtNGU4Zi05M2RjLWUyNTJjZDhkMDI4ZA.jpg"></div><div class="pop-quote-info"><div class="pop-quote-name">Dustin Sparks, <br/>Binary Star</div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-md-4"><div class="pop-quote pop-quote-2 wow rubberBand"><blockquote><p>Super simple to use, very user friendly. Excellent customization designed to fit every/any user/company. Easily send questionnaires, create scorecards, and post jobs that get a lot of activity. I highly recommend.</p></blockquote><div class="pop-quote-person"><div class="pop-quote-avatar"><img src="https://media-exp2.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_400_400/AAEAAQAAAAAAAA1pAAAAJDNiMmZkMGFlLTI3OGQtNDQwOS1iMDA1LTI5ODg2ZTM0NDRmMA.jpg"></div><div class="pop-quote-info"><div class="pop-quote-name">Elyce Murillo, <br/>Linium Resources</div></div></div></div><div class="pop-quote pop-quote-2 wow rubberBand"><blockquote><p>Breezy is a great, easy to use application to streamline my hiring process. I love it!</p></blockquote><div class="pop-quote-person"><div class="pop-quote-avatar"><img src="https://media-exp2.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_400_400/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAv5AAAAJGI5YmE4YjkwLTQ4MTQtNDNmMi04ZGNkLWI5ODE2MDQ0YzQyZA.jpg"></div><div class="pop-quote-info"><div class="pop-quote-name">Courtney Stuart, <br/>Databerries</div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-md-4"><div class="pop-quote pop-quote-3 wow rubberBand"><blockquote><p>I've finally found the recruiting tool I've always wanted in Breezy HR.</p></blockquote><div class="pop-quote-person"><div class="pop-quote-avatar"><img src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/872907690518994944/3n0CakMg_400x400.jpg"></div><div class="pop-quote-info"><div class="pop-quote-name">Wade Foster, <br/>Zapier</div></div></div></div><div class="pop-quote pop-quote-3 wow rubberBand"><blockquote><p>Great user interface, very easy to get started and create a job page for your website as well as instantly blast the job posting out to all the big career sites. There's even a solid mobile app for you to view candidates.</p></blockquote><div class="pop-quote-person"><div class="pop-quote-avatar"><img src="https://media-exp2.licdn.com/mpr/mpr/shrinknp_400_400/AAEAAQAAAAAAAAwLAAAAJDJhNjk4MzI4LWEzMjAtNGMwMi04OGRmLWJlYjc1NjYzMzkzNA.jpg"></div><div class="pop-quote-info"><div class="pop-quote-name">Wilbur Han, <br/>WhereFor</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="features-screenshot-left sourcing"><div class="wow fadeInLeft"><div class="content"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-7 first-md last-xs"><div class="feature-image"><img src="//s3.amazonaws.com/breezyhr-assets/images/marketing/v4/extension-laptop.jpg" alt="Simple Sourcing"></div></div><div class="col-md-5 bigger laptop"><h4>&nbsp;</h4><h2>Source candidates where ever they are, in no time</h2><p>Wherever you find great candidates, you can get them into Breezy. Our Chrome extension lets every employee deliver the best candidates with zero parsing headaches.</p><p>Source candidates in a single click, directly from LinkedIn, Indeed, Xing, Github, AngelList and more!</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class="centered-content soft-green signup-cta"><div class="content"><h1>Smarter hiring decisions are a click away.</h1><p>See how Breezy is helping thousands of companies increase quality &amp; reduce time to hire.</p><div class="row center-xs"><div class="col-md-12 col-xs-12"><form method="GET" action="/signup?greencta"><button type="submit" class="white wow pulse">Get started for free<i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></button><p>Free, easy to set up, no credit card required</p></form></div></div></div></section><section class="features-screenshot-right"><div class="wow fadeInRight"><div class="content"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-5"><br><br><br><h2>Get the whole story of your recruiting efforts</h2><p>Breezy reporting & analytics give you the deep insights you need to power your recruiting process.</p><ul class="list-items"><li><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i